headline.main: Snowmobile Accidents, Deaths Up in Maine This Year
headline.print_headline: Snowmobile Accidents, Deaths Up in Maine This Year

lead_paragraph: Snowmobile accidents and deaths are up in Maine this year as a cold and snowy winter has brought a resurgence of interest in operating the vehicles on the state's many miles of trails.
